  <div id="limitations" class="slide">
    <%= render_partial "h2-link.html", 
      link: "/guides/strategy-limitations#limitations", 
      title: "Limitations" 
    %>

    <p>No strategy is perfect.</p>
    <p>I suppose an important point to note is that there are no silver bullets when it comes to mental health.</p>
    <p>What I mean by this is that there is an inherent communication barrier when it comes to understanding other people's points of view.</p>
    <p>After all, mental health strategies are nothing more than different ways of thinking about your problems.</p>
    <p>The main limitation I face personally is the use of words as a medium to communicate information.</p>
    <p>Words are inherently subjective and so there's a strong level of interpretation that must take place.</p>
    <p>So below are a few more words to hopefully help you maintain perspective.</p>

    <!-- <p>Of course, please keep in mind that there are always limitations to any system, and this is something I address in the <a class="link" href="">strategy limitations</a> section.</p>
